---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
    title="About" 
    description="Learn about Rabbit Holes - a curated collection of beautiful, thought-provoking discoveries from across the internet."
  >
  <div class="container">
    <Header />
    
    <main>
      <div class="about-content">
        <h2>About Rabbit Holes</h2>
        
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>Rabbit Holes is a curated collection of beautiful, thought-provoking discoveries from across the internet. Like Alice tumbling down the rabbit hole, we find ourselves drawn into fascinating worlds of knowledge, art, science, and human creativity.</p>

          <p>Each post is carefully selected for its ability to spark curiosity, offer new perspectives, or simply reveal the extraordinary in the everyday. Whether it's a stunning data visualization, a profound piece of writing, or an unexpected connection between ideas, we share things that make us pause and wonder.</p>

          <p>This is a space for slow discovery—the opposite of endless scrolling. Every link, every story, every image is chosen because it deserves your attention and time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-features">
          <h3>What You'll Find Here</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Curated Content</strong> — Thoughtfully selected discoveries from across the web</li>
            <li><strong>AI-Enhanced Writing</strong> — Posts generated and refined with the help of Claude AI</li>
            <li><strong>Beautiful Design</strong> — Clean, readable typography that respects your attention</li>
            <li><strong>Deep Dives</strong> — Content that rewards careful reading and contemplation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-philosophy">
          <blockquote>
            "The real voyage of discovery consists not in seeking new landscapes, but in having new eyes."
            <cite>— Marcel Proust</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>

        <div class="about-contact">
          <h3>Get in Touch</h3>
          <p>Have something fascinating to share? Found a broken link? Just want to say hello?</p>
          <p>Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@rabbitholes.blog">hello@rabbitholes.blog</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
  }

  body.dark h2 {
    color: var(--text-primary-dark);
  }

  .about-text {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
  }

  body.dark .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-primary-dark);
  }

  .about-features,
  .about-contact {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
  }

  body.dark h3 {
    color: var(--text-primary-dark);
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
  }

  li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--link-light);
  }

  body.dark li {
    color: var(--text-primary-dark);
  }

  body.dark li::before {
    color: var(--link-dark);
  }

  strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
  }

  body.dark strong {
    color: var(--text-primary-dark);
  }

  .about-philosophy {
    margin: 56px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  blockquote {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-secondary-light);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    position: relative;
  }

  body.dark blockquote {
    color: var(--text-secondary-dark);
    background: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-tertiary-light);
  }

  body.dark cite {
    color: var(--text-tertiary-dark);
  }

  .about-contact p {
    color: var(--text-primary-light);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  body.dark .about-contact p {
    color: var(--text-primary-dark);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--link-light);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  body.dark a {
    color: var(--link-dark);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-text {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    blockquote {
      font-size: 20px;
      padding: 32px 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>